 * | `$special_charsnstalled_plugins` | Yes           |  No                | No       | No             |
 * | `$special_charss_ssl`            | Yes           |  Yes               | No       | No             |
 * | `$decompresseddatas`            | Yes           |  Yes               | No       | No             |
 *
 * @since 2.7.0
